yield to provocations" and is "ready to seek ways for establishing
civilized relations with Russia."
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile the Chechen president criticized some people, who do
not want to find a civilized way out of the crisis, referring to
the recent armed attack on a Russian military unit in the
Dagestani town of Buinaksk. 
