<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 2 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on January 3, issued by
China's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. -4 degrees C., max. -2 degrees C., cloudy to
clear, fresh to strong breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 4 degrees C., max. 12 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 25 degrees C., max. 34 degrees C., clear, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Sydney: min. 22 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., cloudy to
overcast, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Karachi: min. 12 degrees C., max. 23 degrees C., clear to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Cairo: min. 10 degrees C., max. 19 degrees C., clear to cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Moscow: min. -4 degrees C., max. -1 degree C., snow shower,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. 3 degrees C., max. 7 degrees C., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 6 degrees C., max. 9 degrees C., drizzle, fresh to
strong breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 5 degrees C., max. 10 degrees C., drizzle,
moderate to fresh breeze.
</P>
<P>
New York: min. -2 degrees C., max. 5 degrees C., clear,
moderate to fresh breeze.  
</P>
