<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, January 2 (Xinhua)-- 875 militants were killed and
900 others arrested along with a large quantity of arms and
ammunition by the army engaged in anti-militancy operations in
India held Jammu and Kashmir in 1997.
</P>
<P>
