market is divided into four zones: transactions, stores,
refrigeration and processing. The annual trade volume is expected
to be five billion yuan (about 600 million US dollars).
</P>
<P>
Operating systems have been set up for agricultural and
side-line products production, purchases and transportation within
the five provinces. An information center also will be set up.
</P>
<P>
