</P>
<P>
According to state radio Thursday, the bombing occurred at the
center of the capital on New Year's Eve, killing one person on the
spot and injured three others.
</P>
<P>
The offender is a soldier from the armed forces of Angola who
has been arrested by the police. (Angola-Bombing)
</P>
